txt.en: A scout has arrived at the entrance to escort you back to Ub Nishir
'Great work here. Those jackals were causing a lot of trouble. Let us return to Ub Nishir.'
Jackals in the furrows scavenge from the dead. It is their nature, but the defiling of fallen allies the coalition cannot abide.
Your mission is to travel to Khaz√¢da and thin the numbers of jackals in the area as well as burn the corpses of slain travellers that have been defiled by the beasts.
